      .i_wrap= image_tag "features/compatibility_icon.png", alt: "Highly compatible"
      %h3.title= "Highly compatible"
      %p= "We've designed SublimeVideo to be highly compatible with your site's existing code, meaning that you don't need to recode a thing to use it."
